Happy birthday to my first Angel that came to this world to change my life forever happy 11th birthday @kingferran TE AMO

Thanks to my event planner for bringing all my vision to live you are the sweetest hard working mama that I ever met .

Event planner 👉🏻👉🏻 @playplayzone 

Photografer 👉🏻 @amberrainphotography 

Thanks to all the vendors I love you all 
 
Slime table 👉🏻@little_artist_party 
Paleta car 👉🏻@playplaypaletas
Chilli gummies 👉🏻@ositos_addict 
Balloons 👉🏻@graceand_confetti 
Flowers👉🏻@bohemianblooms_byus 
Customized candy 👉🏻@blowup.l.a 
Cake&deserts 👉🏻@sweetconfetti_1
